        <i18n>
            <description lang="en"><![CDATA[In Fiavè, in a central position, we offer for rent an independent house consisting of a three-room apartment and a large cellar room.
    The property has undergone a very recent energy redevelopment, with the construction of a thermal coat, replacement of the fixtures and the boiler and installation of a solar thermal system.
    The apartment is spread over two levels and is composed as follows: on the first floor living area, with the possibility of installing a pellet stove, small bathroom and access staircase to the second floor; on the second floor double bedroom, single bedroom with access to the balcony and bathroom with window. The spaces are completed by a large cellar on the ground floor.
    No condominium fees.
    Long term contracts only.]]></description>
            <title lang="en"><![CDATA[Three-room apartment in an independent house]]></title>
